。<br><br><span style="color: rgb(28, 187, 180);"><strong>不管你是技术大佬，还是零(未)基(来)础(的)同(大)学(佬)，我们都真诚欢迎你的加入！</strong></span></p></div></section></div><div class="tn-comp-anim-pin tn-comp tn-from-house-paper-cp ng-scope" tn-comp-pose="compConstraint.pose.tplPose || compAttr.pose" tn-uuid="" tn-animate="(!isCompBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : compAttr.anim)" style="" tn-ra-comp="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:2.col1:1"><section class="tn-comp-pin tn-comp-style-pin" tn-link="compAttr.link || comp.link" tn-sound="compAttr.sound" tn-pre-load-image="compAttr.style.backgroundImage"><div style="text-align:justify;" tn-cell-type="text" class="tn-cell tn-cell-text tn-child-position-absolute horizontal-tb tn-state-active ng-scope" tn-link="cell.link" tn-animate="(!isCellBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : cell.anim)" tn-animate-on-self="true" tn-sound="cell.sound" tn-yzk-font-usage-id="cell.style.tnYzkFontUsageId" title="" tn-ra-cell="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:2.col1:1.txt1"><p><br></p></div></section></div> </div></section>
            <section v-if="resultIndex === 2" class="tn-comp-pin tn-comp-style-pin" tn-link="compAttr.link || comp.link" tn-sound="compAttr.sound" tn-pre-load-image="compAttr.style.backgroundImage" style="text-align: right;"><div style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top;  padding: 10px; border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);" tn-cell-type="group" class="tn-cell tn-cell-group tn-child-position-static tn-state-active ng-scope" tn-link="cell.link" tn-animate="(!isCellBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : cell.anim)" tn-animate-on-self="true" tn-sound="cell.sound" tn-ra-cell="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:3.col1"> <div class="tn-comp-anim-pin tn-comp tn-from-house-paper-cp ng-scope" tn-comp-pose="compConstraint.pose.tplPose || compAttr.pose" tn-uuid="" tn-animate="(!isCompBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : compAttr.anim)" style="" tn-ra-comp="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:3.col1:0"><section class="tn-comp-pin tn-comp-style-pin" tn-link="compAttr.link || comp.link" tn-sound="compAttr.sound" tn-pre-load-image="compAttr.style.backgroundImage"><div style="text-align:justify;" tn-cell-type="text" class="tn-cell tn-cell-text tn-child-position-absolute horizontal-tb tn-state-active ng-scope" tn-link="cell.link" tn-animate="(!isCellBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : cell.anim)" tn-animate-on-self="true" tn-sound="cell.sound" tn-yzk-font-usage-id="cell.style.tnYzkFontUsageId" title="" tn-ra-cell="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:3.col1:0.txt1"><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 93.75%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">热爱游戏，崇尚体育精神？</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 93.75%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">充满创意，喜欢制造乐趣？</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 93.75%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">满脑子奇奇怪怪的新想法，想解锁形形色色的新技能？</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 93.75%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">欢迎加入赛事部！</span></strong></p></div></section></div><div class="tn-comp-anim-pin tn-comp tn-from-house-paper-cp ng-scope" tn-comp-pose="compConstraint.pose.tplPose || compAttr.pose" tn-uuid="" tn-animate="(!isCompBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : compAttr.anim)" style="" tn-ra-comp="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:3.col1:1"><section class="tn-comp-pin tn-comp-style-pin" tn-link="compAttr.link || comp.link" tn-sound="compAttr.sound" tn-pre-load-image="compAttr.style.backgroundImage"><div style="text-align:justify;" tn-cell-type="text" class="tn-cell tn-cell-text tn-child-position-absolute horizontal-tb tn-state-active ng-scope" tn-link="cell.link" tn-animate="(!isCellBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : cell.anim)" tn-animate-on-self="true" tn-sound="cell.sound" tn-yzk-font-usage-id="cell.style.tnYzkFontUsageId" title="" tn-ra-cell="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:3.col1:1.txt1"><p><br></p></div></section></div><div class="tn-comp-anim-pin tn-comp tn-from-house-paper-cp ng-scope" tn-comp-pose="compConstraint.pose.tplPose || compAttr.pose" tn-uuid="" tn-animate="(!isCompBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : compAttr.anim)" style="" tn-ra-comp="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:3.col1:2"><section class="tn-comp-pin tn-comp-style-pin" tn-link="compAttr.link || comp.link" tn-sound="compAttr.sound" tn-pre-load-image="compAttr.style.backgroundImage"><div style="text-align:justify;" tn-cell-type="text" class="tn-cell tn-cell-text tn-child-position-absolute horizontal-tb tn-state-active ng-scope" tn-link="cell.link" tn-animate="(!isCellBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : cell.anim)" tn-animate-on-self="true" tn-sound="cell.sound" tn-yzk-font-usage-id="cell.style.tnYzkFontUsageId" title="" tn-ra-cell="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:3.col1:2.txt1"><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 93.75%;">来赛事部，做认真的玩家 —— <strong>游戏</strong>总是占据着赛事部的核心地位。</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 93.75%;">头脑风暴、策划、开发、试玩、美工一条龙，这里将给你充足的机会去打造一个心目中理想的电子游戏；命题、选题、组织、宣传、主持连环阵，这里将给你无限的空间去设计一场紧张刺激的知识竞赛。用力工作用力玩，不想工作就快乐地玩一场，也是一种提升呢。</span></p></div></section></div><div class="tn-comp-anim-pin tn-comp tn-from-house-paper-cp ng-scope" tn-comp-pose="compConstraint.pose.tplPose || compAttr.pose" tn-uuid="" tn-animate="(!isCompBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : compAttr.anim)" style="" tn-ra-comp="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:3.col1:3"><section class="tn-comp-pin tn-comp-style-pin" tn-link="compAttr.link || comp.link" tn-sound="compAttr.sound" tn-pre-load-image="compAttr.style.backgroundImage"><div style="text-align:justify;" tn-cell-type="text" class="tn-cell tn-cell-text tn-child-position-absolute horizontal-tb tn-state-active ng-scope" tn-link="cell.link" tn-animate="(!isCellBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : cell.anim)" tn-animate-on-self="true" tn-sound="cell.sound" tn-yzk-font-usage-id="cell.style.tnYzkFontUsageId" title="" tn-ra-cell="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:3.col1:3.txt1"><p><br></p></div></section></div><div class="tn-comp-anim-pin tn-comp tn-from-house-paper-cp ng-scope" tn-comp-pose="compConstraint.pose.tplPose || compAttr.pose" tn-uuid="" tn-animate="(!isCompBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : compAttr.anim)" style="" tn-ra-comp="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:3.col1:4"><section class="tn-comp-pin tn-comp-style-pin" tn-link="compAttr.link || comp.link" tn-sound="compAttr.sound" tn-pre-load-image="compAttr.style.backgroundImage" style=""><div style="text-align: left; font-size: 93.75%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.6;" tn-cell-type="text" class="tn-cell tn-cell-text tn-child-position-absolute horizontal-tb tn-state-active ng-scope" tn-link="cell.link" tn-animate="(!isCellBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : cell.anim)" tn-animate-on-self="true" tn-sound="cell.sound" tn-yzk-font-usage-id="cell.style.tnYzkFontUsageId" title="" tn-ra-cell="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:3.col1:4.txt1"><p>来赛事部，助力品牌腾飞 ——&nbsp;<strong>GStrategy 游戏竞赛</strong>是赛事部本学期的主营业务，是我们倾力打造的新兴品牌。</p><p>面对一个并不复杂却变化多端的游戏，选手们设计策略并编写程序互相对抗，在战斗过程中吸取经验，不断改进，打造各自的“不败智能体”。赛事部与学院的《离散数学 (2)》课程合作，将学习内容与比赛结合，并作为课程作业的选项之一，同时设置了丰富的物质奖励。举办竞赛是复杂的工作，不仅需要创意和技术，也需要统筹安排与人际沟通，更需要细心设计选手和观众的参与体验；只要愿意，总有一个地方等待着你的贡献。</p></div></section></div><div class="tn-comp-anim-pin tn-comp tn-from-house-paper-cp ng-scope" tn-comp-pose="compConstraint.pose.tplPose || compAttr.pose" tn-uuid="" tn-animate="(!isCompBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : compAttr.anim)" style="" tn-ra-comp="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:3.col1:5"><section class="tn-comp-pin tn-comp-style-pin" tn-link="compAttr.link || comp.link" tn-sound="compAttr.sound" tn-pre-load-image="compAttr.style.backgroundImage" style=""><div style="text-align:justify;" tn-cell-type="text" class="tn-cell tn-cell-text tn-child-position-absolute horizontal-tb tn-state-active ng-scope" tn-link="cell.link" tn-animate="(!isCellBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : cell.anim)" tn-animate-on-self="true" tn-sound="cell.sound" tn-yzk-font-usage-id="cell.style.tnYzkFontUsageId" title="" tn-ra-cell="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:3.col1:5.txt1"><p><br></p></div></section></div><div class="tn-comp-anim-pin tn-comp tn-from-house-paper-cp ng-scope" tn-comp-pose="compConstraint.pose.tplPose || compAttr.pose" tn-uuid="" tn-animate="(!isCompBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : compAttr.anim)" style="" tn-ra-comp="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:3.col1:6"><section class="tn-comp-pin tn-comp-style-pin" tn-link="compAttr.link || comp.link" tn-sound="compAttr.sound" tn-pre-load-image="compAttr.style.backgroundImage" style=""><div style="text-align:justify;" tn-cell-type="text" class="tn-cell tn-cell-text tn-child-position-absolute horizontal-tb tn-state-active ng-scope" tn-link="cell.link" tn-animate="(!isCellBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : cell.anim)" tn-animate-on-self="true" tn-sound="cell.sound" tn-yzk-font-usage-id="cell.style.tnYzkFontUsageId" title="" tn-ra-cell="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:3.col1:6.txt1"><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 93.75%;">来赛事部，解锁无限可能 —— 赛事部的工作总是充满着意料之外的<strong>惊喜</strong>。</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 93.75%;">在手机上试验游戏原型，制作网页用于播放游戏记录，甚至设计学生节抽奖程序，五花八门的小任务是赛事部的技术日常，使得这里成为了尝试新鲜事物的实验室。这里将让你接触更多开发的新技术，沉迷于各种有趣的小玩意儿，亦能为未来面对的工作打开更广阔的思路，成为开发者中一个有趣的灵魂。</span></p></div></section></div><div class="tn-comp-anim-pin tn-comp tn-from-house-paper-cp ng-scope" tn-comp-pose="compConstraint.pose.tplPose || compAttr.pose" tn-uuid="" tn-animate="(!isCompBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : compAttr.anim)" style="" tn-ra-comp="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:3.col1:7"><section class="tn-comp-pin tn-comp-style-pin" tn-link="compAttr.link || comp.link" tn-sound="compAttr.sound" tn-pre-load-image="compAttr.style.backgroundImage" style=""><div style="text-align:justify;" tn-cell-type="text" class="tn-cell tn-cell-text tn-child-position-absolute horizontal-tb tn-state-active ng-scope" tn-link="cell.link" tn-animate="(!isCellBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : cell.anim)" tn-animate-on-self="true" tn-sound="cell.sound" tn-yzk-font-usage-id="cell.style.tnYzkFontUsageId" title="" tn-ra-cell="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:3.col1:7.txt1"><p><br></p></div></section></div><div class="tn-comp-anim-pin tn-comp tn-from-house-paper-cp ng-scope" tn-comp-pose="compConstraint.pose.tplPose || compAttr.pose" tn-uuid="" tn-animate="(!isCompBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : compAttr.anim)" style="" tn-ra-comp="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:3.col1:8"><section class="tn-comp-pin tn-comp-style-pin" tn-link="compAttr.link || comp.link" tn-sound="compAttr.sound" tn-pre-load-image="compAttr.style.backgroundImage" style=""><div style="text-align: left; font-size: 93.75%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.6;" tn-cell-type="text" class="tn-cell tn-cell-text tn-child-position-absolute horizontal-tb tn-state-active ng-scope" tn-link="cell.link" tn-animate="(!isCellBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : cell.anim)" tn-animate-on-self="true" tn-sound="cell.sound" tn-yzk-font-usage-id="cell.style.tnYzkFontUsageId" title="" tn-ra-cell="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:3.col1:8.txt1"><p>另外，如果你同时还喜欢 QQ 糖，那么真是来对地方了。<br></p><p><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(243, 123, 29);"><strong>赛事部期待你的到来！</strong></span></p></div></section></div> </div></section>
            <section v-if="resultIndex === 3" class="tn-comp-pin tn-comp-style-pin" tn-link="compAttr.link || comp.link" tn-sound="compAttr.sound" tn-pre-load-image="compAttr.style.backgroundImage" style="text-align: right;"><div style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top;  padding: 10px; border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;" tn-cell-type="group" class="tn-cell tn-cell-group tn-child-position-static tn-state-active ng-scope" tn-link="cell.link" tn-animate="(!isCellBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : cell.anim)" tn-animate-on-self="true" tn-sound="cell.sound" tn-ra-cell="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:4.col1"> <div class="tn-comp-anim-pin tn-comp tn-from-house-paper-cp ng-scope" tn-comp-pose="compConstraint.pose.tplPose || compAttr.pose" tn-uuid="" tn-animate="(!isCompBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : compAttr.anim)" style="" tn-ra-comp="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:4.col1:0"><section class="tn-comp-pin tn-comp-style-pin" tn-link="compAttr.link || comp.link" tn-sound="compAttr.sound" tn-pre-load-image="compAttr.style.backgroundImage"><div style="text-align:justify;" tn-cell-type="text" class="tn-cell tn-cell-text tn-child-position-absolute horizontal-tb tn-state-active ng-scope" tn-link="cell.link" tn-animate="(!isCellBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : cell.anim)" tn-animate-on-self="true" tn-sound="cell.sound" tn-yzk-font-usage-id="cell.style.tnYzkFontUsageId" title="" tn-ra-cell="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:4.col1:0.txt1"><p>项目部的关键词是什么？<strong>没错，是“科创”！</strong>我们就是院系科创的引领者。</p><p><br></p><p style="">在这里，我们全程筹备院系定制科研训练计划SSRT，招募热爱科研的同学走进实验室，挑战科学之巅。从策划到宣传，从筹备到组织，你将亲自见证举办一场院系级活动的全过程。</p><p><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/wsLJOeOEwohOwjznfbfasQ">SSRT初审报名详情</a></p><p><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/kO_cWG8xwtlOvPzz9DqFCg">SSRT终审和挑战杯初审现场实录</a></p></div></section></div><div class="tn-comp-anim-pin tn-comp tn-from-house-paper-cp ng-scope" tn-comp-pose="compConstraint.pose.tplPose || compAttr.pose" tn-uuid="" tn-animate="(!isCompBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : compAttr.anim)" style="" tn-ra-comp="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:4.col1:1"><section class="tn-comp-pin tn-comp-style-pin" tn-link="compAttr.link || comp.link" tn-sound="compAttr.sound" tn-pre-load-image="compAttr.style.backgroundImage"><div style="text-align:justify;" tn-cell-type="text" class="tn-cell tn-cell-text tn-child-position-absolute horizontal-tb tn-state-active ng-scope" tn-link="cell.link" tn-animate="(!isCellBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : cell.anim)" tn-animate-on-self="true" tn-sound="cell.sound" tn-yzk-font-usage-id="cell.style.tnYzkFontUsageId" title="" tn-ra-cell="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:4.col1:1.txt1"><p><br></p></div></section></div><div class="tn-comp-anim-pin tn-comp tn-from-house-paper-cp ng-scope" tn-comp-pose="compConstraint.pose.tplPose || compAttr.pose" tn-uuid="" tn-animate="(!isCompBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : compAttr.anim)" style="" tn-ra-comp="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:4.col1:2"><section class="tn-comp-pin tn-comp-style-pin" tn-link="compAttr.link || comp.link" tn-sound="compAttr.sound" tn-pre-load-image="compAttr.style.backgroundImage" style=""><div style="text-align:justify;" tn-cell-type="text" class="tn-cell tn-cell-text tn-child-position-absolute horizontal-tb tn-state-active ng-scope" tn-link="cell.link" tn-animate="(!isCellBound ? '__NOT_MOUNT__' : cell.anim)" tn-animate-on-self="true" tn-sound="cell.sound" tn-yzk-font-usage-id="cell.style.tnYzkFontUsageId" title="" tn-ra-cell="box.cubes:0.pages:0.layers:0.comps:4.col1:2.txt1"><p style="">在这里，我们与校科协紧密合作，承办挑战杯，为热爱科创的参赛者搭建展示的平台。每年校庆之际，我们参与组织“挑战杯”竞赛优秀作品展，为我们院系的展位做好宣传和后勤工作。在校科展上，你将有机会与同样热爱科创的全校大牛充分交流，零距离感受高水平科创项目，体会其独特的魅力。</p><p><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/Ifp4RQdj82Q9mnH4lS6syQ">软院同学在挑战杯上斩获佳绩</a></p><p><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/eMxUwMXcz_n2vH0q4ozi-A" style="background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);">软院同学的项目在校科展上展示</a></p></div></section></div><div class="tn-co